ActPilotage Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of EDWARD F. ANTHONY of St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, as a member of the Atlantic Pilotage Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Donald Hugh Duffy, effective September 12, 2009.
